## 🔄 GIT WORKFLOW

### Commit Messages
```
feat: Add backload listing creation
fix: Resolve offer notification bug  
refactor: Extract transport calculation logic
style: Update button hover states
docs: Add API documentation
```

### Branch Strategy
- `master` - Production
- `develop` - Development
- `feature/*` - New features
- `fix/*` - Bug fixes

