- Complex business logic (why, not just what)
- Database schema changes
- Environment variable changes
- Breaking changes

### Code Comments
```typescript
// ❌ Bad: Increment counter
count++

// ✅ Good: Track active user sessions for analytics dashboard
activeUserSessions++

// ✅ Good: Calculate platform fee (R1/ton as per pricing model)
const platformFee = quantity * 1
```

